sentence: please show me all first class flights , from los angeles to minneapolis on thursday afternoon
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  v0.departure_time, '"'||v1.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v5.days_code||'"', '"'||v6.day_name||'"', v6.year,
 v6.month_number, v6.day_number, '"'||v7.flight_id||'"', '"'||v8.fare_id||'"',
 '"'||v9.fare_basis_code||'"', '"'||v9.class_type||'"',
 '"'||v10.fare_basis_code||'"', '"'||v11.days_code||'"',
 '"'||v12.day_name||'"', v12.year, v12.month_number,
 v12.day_number FROM flight v0, airport_service v1, city v2,
 airport_service v3, city v4, days v5, date_day v6, flight_fare v7,
 fare v8, fare_basis v9, fare_basis v10, days v11, date_day v12 
WHERE ((v0.departure_time BETWEEN  1200 AND  1800) 
AND (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) 
AND (v2.city_name = 'LOS ANGELES'))) 
AND (((v0.to_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) 
AND (v4.city_name = 'MINNEAPOLIS'))) 
AND (((v0.flight_days = ANY v5.days_code) AND ((v5.day_name = ANY v6.day_name) 
AND (((v6.year =  1993) AND (v6.month_number =  7)) 
AND (v6.day_number =  29)))) AND ((v0.flight_id = ANY v7.flight_id) 
AND ((v7.fare_id = ANY v8.fare_id) 
AND (((v8.fare_basis_code = ANY v9.fare_basis_code) AND (v9.class_type = 'FIRST')) 
AND ((v8.fare_basis_code = ANY v10.fare_basis_code) 
AND ((v10.basis_days = ANY v11.days_code) AND ((v11.day_name = ANY v12.day_name) 
AND (((v12.year =  1993) 
AND (v12.month_number =  7)) AND (v12.day_number =  29))))))))))));

FLIGHT_ID IN ( SELECT FLIGHT_FARE . FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT_FARE WHERE FLIGHT_FARE . FARE_ID IN ( SELECT FARE .
